      <title>美国银行的门萨表示利率不会回到疫情前的水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/bofa-s-mensah-says-rates-won-t-return-to-levels-before-pandemic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行的伯纳德·门萨表示，由于地缘政治冲突、供应链变化等摩擦困扰着全球经济，世界许多地区的利率可能仍将维持在高位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/bofa-s-mensah-says-rates-won-t-return-to-levels-before-pandemic</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 08:38:47 GMT</pubDate>
