      <title>股市狂热刺激需求，港元供应收紧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hong-kong-dollar-supply-tightens-as-stocks-frenzy-boosts-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于本地股市上涨和季节性因素，港元供应收紧，推动港元兑美元汇率升至最高水平。]]></description>
