    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚第二季度经济增长放缓至 2022 年最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/kenya-s-economic-growth-slows-to-2022-low-in-second-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一系列针对高生活成本的抗议活动影响了产出和消费者支出，肯尼亚第二季度经济增长率跌至 18 个月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/kenya-s-economic-growth-slows-to-2022-low-in-second-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 07:57:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德在创纪录的印度市场追逐私人信贷交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/blackrock-chases-private-credit-deals-in-growing-indian-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着印度蓬勃发展的私人信贷市场吸引了更多的借款人，全球最大的资产管理公司贝莱德公司 (BlackRock Inc.) 正在从农业到酒店业等越来越多的行业中寻找印度直接贷款机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/blackrock-chases-private-credit-deals-in-growing-indian-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 07:51:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳新银行首席执行官埃利奥特称对中国的担忧“被严重夸大了”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/china-fears-are-massively-overblown-anz-ceo-elliott-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳新银行集团控股有限公司首席执行官 Shayne Elliott 表示，对于“中国不再是投资目的地”的担忧“被严重夸大了”，因为该银行看到中国业务蓬勃发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/china-fears-are-massively-overblown-anz-ceo-elliott-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 06:26:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受刺激政策押注推动，中国股市在香港飙升逾 7%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/chinese-stocks-in-hong-kong-rise-as-traders-return-from-holiday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着刺激计划引发的热情席卷香港 5.8 万亿美元的市场，在香港上市的中国股票创下近两年来最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/chinese-stocks-in-hong-kong-rise-as-traders-return-from-holiday</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 01:29:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
